      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白，起点用圆角矩形表示rule_description，然后箭头指向WS节点。WS是workflow_setup的缩写对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "rule_description",
        "workflow_setup"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，WS就是workflow_setup。接下来要分叉，先到similar_rule_analyzer分析相似规则，再到schema_and_sample_events_analyzer做Schema和样本事件分析。",
      "elements_involved": [
