      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这两个分析节点是菱形判断框吗？而且它们之间是什么关系，串行还是并行？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "similar_rule_analyzer",
        "schema_and_sample_events_analyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "串行的，先SRA后SSEA，都是判断节点用菱形。但有个特殊逻辑：这两个分析都有可能跳过，如果不需要的话直接走虚线到rule_creator。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "similar_rule_analyzer",
        "schema_and_sample_events_analyzer",
        "rule_creator"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画好了SRA到SSEA的实线，以及SRA和SSEA各自到RC的虚线，标注\"Skip if not needed\"。然后RC是rule_creator，矩形节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "similar_rule_analyzer",
        "schema_and_sample_events_analyzer",
        "rule_creator"
